			"_type_note": "New step type — not yet in schema v1.0. Must be added to valid type enum before CI will pass. Two phases: (1) build_sequence — Byte constructs the skeleton token by token with narration. (2) drag_label — three sticky notes, three drop zones. No hearts at risk. No XP. Wrong drop bounces the note back — no error state, no mistake_log write. All three correct → snap animation → Byte celebrates → advances. See design notes in lesson MD for full implementation spec.",
